# AEM Portfolio

Before any task, read `instructions.md` for AEM, Git, and docs facts.

- Repo: `devistic-asim/aem-portfolio`
- Site slug: `aem-portfolio`
- Never modify `scripts/aem.js`
- Code in Git; content in da.live via Sidekick (local: `drafts/`)
- Dark theme tokens in `styles/styles.css`
- Lint: `npm run lint` | Dev: `npm run dev`
- PRs require preview URL on `*.aem.page`

Use specialized agents in `.cursor/agents/` for blocks, content, site admin, git, and docs.
